		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>You toss a splash of water and dust in the air, and the droplets freeze around the dust and grow into hailstorms of rock-hard ice that pound down to the ground in a localized storm.</em></p><p><strong>[[/save dexterity]]{Dexterity Save}</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target takes [[/damage 2d8 bludgeoning]] damage* + [[/damage 4d6 cold]] damage</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Half damage.</p></li><li><p><strong>Hazard:</strong> The area is &amp;reference[difficult terrain] till the end of your next turn.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>*</strong> <strong>Upcasting:</strong> Increase bludgeoning damage by [[/damage 1d8 bludgeoning]]{1d8} for each spell level above 4th.</p>",
